        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Maven-基础篇"><a href="#Maven-基础篇" class="headerlink" title="Maven 基础篇"></a><em>Maven 基础篇</em></h2><h3 id="maven简介："><a href="#maven简介：" class="headerlink" title="maven简介："></a>maven简介：</h3><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/CM4HNM5Z/image-20221213225428988.png" alt="maven的简介"></p><h4 id="maven项目结构的介绍："><a href="#maven项目结构的介绍：" class="headerlink" title="maven项目结构的介绍："></a>maven项目结构的介绍：</h4><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/cL658tsM/image-20221213230116022.png" alt="temp"></p><h4 id="maven-的依赖管理"><a href="#maven-的依赖管理" class="headerlink" title="maven 的依赖管理"></a>maven 的依赖管理</h4><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/Dy1PwmC0/image-20221213235637602.png" alt="image-20221213235637602"></p><h5 id="仓库的介绍："><a href="#仓库的介绍：" class="headerlink" title="仓库的介绍："></a>仓库的介绍：</h5><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/jjyDzJ7n/image-20221214000311293.png" alt="image-20221214000311293"></p><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/wvVcQrmN/image-20221214000538632.png" alt="image-20221214000538632"></p><h4 id="快捷键生成依赖：-ALT-INSERT"><a href="#快捷键生成依赖：-ALT-INSERT" class="headerlink" title="快捷键生成依赖： ALT + INSERT"></a>快捷键生成依赖： ALT + INSERT</h4><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/0QqynSXS/image-20221214114853548.png" alt="image-20221214114853548"></p><h4 id="依赖范围"><a href="#依赖范围" class="headerlink" title="依赖范围"></a>依赖范围</h4><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/76xybnQK/image-20221214115348977.png" alt="image-20221214115348977"></p><h2 id="maven的下载安装及配置"><a href="#maven的下载安装及配置" class="headerlink" title="maven的下载安装及配置"></a>maven的下载安装及配置</h2><h5 id="参考网上博客：Maven安装与配置教程-IT学长的博客-CSDN博客-mvn-安装配置"><a href="#参考网上博客：Maven安装与配置教程-IT学长的博客-CSDN博客-mvn-安装配置" class="headerlink" title="参考网上博客：Maven安装与配置教程_IT学长的博客-CSDN博客_mvn 安装配置"></a>参考网上博客：<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_40625778/article/details/125229241?ops_request_misc=%7B%22request_id%22:%22167094139716782395314173%22,%22scm%22:%2220140713.130102334..%22%7D&request_id=167094139716782395314173&biz_id=0&utm_medium=distribute.pc_search_result.none-task-blog-2~all~top_positive~default-4-125229241-null-null.142%5Ev68%5Econtrol,201%5Ev4%5Eadd_ask,213%5Ev2%5Et3_control2&utm_term=maven%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%B8%8E%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE&spm=1018.2226.3001.4187">Maven安装与配置教程_IT学长的博客-CSDN博客_mvn 安装配置</a></h5><h4 id="黑马程序员：03-Maven安装-amp-配置及基本使用-哔哩哔哩-bilibili"><a href="#黑马程序员：03-Maven安装-amp-配置及基本使用-哔哩哔哩-bilibili" class="headerlink" title="黑马程序员：03-Maven安装&amp;配置及基本使用_哔哩哔哩_bilibili"></a>黑马程序员：<a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Qf4y1T7Hx/?p=44&spm_id_from=pageDriver&vd_source=7905ca4d33f9e55dec19fa0b64248cc2">03-Maven安装&amp;配置及基本使用_哔哩哔哩_bilibili</a></h4><h2 id="maven的生命周期"><a href="#maven的生命周期" class="headerlink" title="maven的生命周期"></a>maven的生命周期</h2><h4 id="示意图："><a href="#示意图：" class="headerlink" title="示意图："></a>示意图：</h4><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/NFy8sgdx/image-20221214103612704.png" alt="image-20221214103612704"></p><h2 id="maven在IDEA中的配置"><a href="#maven在IDEA中的配置" class="headerlink" title="maven在IDEA中的配置"></a>maven在IDEA中的配置</h2><h4 id="IDEA-配置maven环境"><a href="#IDEA-配置maven环境" class="headerlink" title="IDEA 配置maven环境"></a>IDEA 配置maven环境</h4><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/5yQmbwg0/image-20221214111129837.png" alt="image-20221214111129837"></p><h5 id="maven的坐标"><a href="#maven的坐标" class="headerlink" title="maven的坐标"></a>maven的坐标</h5><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/g0vjFr3W/image-20221214111410932.png" alt="image-20221214111410932"></p><h4 id="maven创建项目"><a href="#maven创建项目" class="headerlink" title="maven创建项目"></a>maven创建项目</h4><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/7ZNPmj4H/image-20221214111716424.png" alt="image-20221214111716424"></p><h4 id="idea导入maven项目"><a href="#idea导入maven项目" class="headerlink" title="idea导入maven项目"></a>idea导入maven项目</h4><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/gJyP2Z0Y/image-20221214112004928.png" alt="image-20221214112004928"></p><h4 id="IDEA-安装Maven-Helper插件"><a href="#IDEA-安装Maven-Helper插件" class="headerlink" title="IDEA 安装Maven-Helper插件"></a>IDEA 安装Maven-Helper插件</h4><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/d19tSXrm/image-20221214112527717.png" alt="image-20221214112527717"></p><h2 id="MyBatis持久层框架"><a href="#MyBatis持久层框架" class="headerlink" title="MyBatis持久层框架"></a><em>MyBatis持久层框架</em></h2><h4 id="MyBatis框架是什么"><a href="#MyBatis框架是什么" class="headerlink" title="MyBatis框架是什么"></a>MyBatis框架是什么</h4><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/v8xktjFp/image-20221214121746270.png" alt="image-20221214121746270"></p><h4 id="JDBC-的缺点（繁琐）"><a href="#JDBC-的缺点（繁琐）" class="headerlink" title="JDBC 的缺点（繁琐）"></a>JDBC 的缺点（繁琐）</h4><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/PxwyYgpy/image-20221214122044195.png" alt="image-20221214122044195"></p><h4 id="MyBatis-简化"><a href="#MyBatis-简化" class="headerlink" title="MyBatis 简化"></a>MyBatis 简化</h4><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/hjYFtRF0/image-20221214122357004.png" alt="image-20221214122357004"></p><h3 id="MyBatis-框架"><a href="#MyBatis-框架" class="headerlink" title="MyBatis 框架"></a>MyBatis 框架</h3><ul><li>MyBatis 快速入门</li></ul><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/k4J8XLND/image-20221214123153365.png" alt="image-20221214123153365"></p><p>入门心得：</p><blockquote><p>还是那句话，mysql版本8.+的，配置文件写法为：（写在java目录下的resource文件下）</p><figure class="highlight properties"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">driver</span>=<span class="string">com.mysql.cj.jdbc.Driver</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">url</span>=<span class="string">jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/lby_db01?useSSL=false&amp;serverTimezone=GMT&amp;characterEncoding=utf-8&amp;autoReconnect=true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">username</span>=<span class="string">root</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">password</span>=<span class="string">123456</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在mybatis-config.xml配置文件中引入properties的前提是，在 配置文件中加入这句</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">properties</span> <span class="attr">resource</span>=<span class="string">&quot;db.properties&quot;</span> &gt;</span> <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">properties</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>mybatis-config.xml的配置文件为：</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?xml version=<span class="string">&quot;1.0&quot;</span> encoding=<span class="string">&quot;UTF-8&quot;</span> ?&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;!DOCTYPE <span class="keyword">configuration</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">        <span class="keyword">PUBLIC</span> <span class="string">&quot;-//mybatis.org//DTD Config 3.0//EN&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">        <span class="string">&quot;https://mybatis.org/dtd/mybatis-3-config.dtd&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">configuration</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">properties</span> <span class="attr">resource</span>=<span class="string">&quot;db.properties&quot;</span> &gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">properties</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">environments</span> <span class="attr">default</span>=<span class="string">&quot;development&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">environment</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">&quot;development&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">transactionManager</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;JDBC&quot;</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dataSource</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;POOLED&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">property</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;driver&quot;</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot;$&#123;driver&#125;&quot;</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">property</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;url&quot;</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot;$&#123;url&#125;&quot;</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">property</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;username&quot;</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot;$&#123;username&#125;&quot;</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">property</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;password&quot;</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot;$&#123;password&#125;&quot;</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dataSource</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">environment</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">environments</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">mappers</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">mapper</span> <span class="attr">resource</span>=<span class="string">&quot;com/mapper/UserMapper.xml&quot;</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">mappers</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">configuration</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>mapper.xml文件的配置（编写sql语句）</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?xml version=<span class="string">&quot;1.0&quot;</span> encoding=<span class="string">&quot;UTF-8&quot;</span> ?&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;!DOCTYPE <span class="keyword">mapper</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">        <span class="keyword">PUBLIC</span> <span class="string">&quot;-//mybatis.org//DTD Mapper 3.0//EN&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">        <span class="string">&quot;https://mybatis.org/dtd/mybatis-3-mapper.dtd&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!--</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">namespace: 名称标签</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">mapper</span> <span class="attr">namespace</span>=<span class="string">&quot;com.mapper.UserMapper&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">select</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">&quot;selectAll&quot;</span> <span class="attr">resultType</span>=<span class="string">&quot;com.pojo.User&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        select * from student;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">select</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">mapper</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><ul><li><p>Mapper 代理开发</p><p>mapper.xml文件中红色警告的解决，</p><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/B6MRb8yD/image-20221214133822941.png" alt="image-20221214133822941"></p></li></ul><blockquote><p>根据上述步骤配置数据库又出意外，原因就是，MySQL的版本高，需要设置时区</p><p>解决方法：（<strong>用了这么久的IDEA才发现它这么厉害，太强了呜呜呜</strong>）</p><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/wvHJj2Rf/image-20221214135743985.png"></p></blockquote><p>代理步骤一（将mapper 类和 mapper.xml文件处于同一个目录下）：</p><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/dtR4d17d/image-20221214145313796.png" alt="image-20221214145313796"></p><ul><li>MyBatis 核心配置文件</li></ul><p> MyBatis的核心配置文件需要遵循一下顺序，不能颠倒顺序</p><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/qM5Dp7Fd/image-20221214155954738.png" alt="image-20221214155954738"></p><p>MyBatisX插件的使用</p><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/rwLD7190/image-20221214161130974.png" alt="image-20221214161130974"></p><ul><li>注解完成增删改查</li></ul><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/7YyJf5sy/image-20221214165406282.png" alt="image-20221214165406282"></p><h5 id="举例-："><a href="#举例-：" class="headerlink" title="举例 ："></a>举例 ：</h5><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 这里是接口中的方法</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Select(&quot;select * from student where id = #&#123;id&#125;&quot;)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> Student <span class="title function_">selectById</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> id)</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>动态 SQL</li></ul><h3 id="注：数据库表的字段名和-pojo实体类中的属性名称不一样时，不能自动封装数据"><a href="#注：数据库表的字段名和-pojo实体类中的属性名称不一样时，不能自动封装数据" class="headerlink" title="注：数据库表的字段名和 pojo实体类中的属性名称不一样时，不能自动封装数据"></a><em>注：数据库表的字段名和 pojo实体类中的属性名称不一样时，不能自动封装数据</em></h3><h3 id="解决方案："><a href="#解决方案：" class="headerlink" title="解决方案："></a>解决方案：</h3><h5 id="1-1-给不相同的数据库表的字段名起别名（如下面sql片段那样起别名）"><a href="#1-1-给不相同的数据库表的字段名起别名（如下面sql片段那样起别名）" class="headerlink" title="1.1. 给不相同的数据库表的字段名起别名（如下面sql片段那样起别名）"></a>1.1. 给不相同的数据库表的字段名起别名（如下面sql片段那样起别名）</h5><h5 id="1-2-使用-sql-片段，第一次听说"><a href="#1-2-使用-sql-片段，第一次听说" class="headerlink" title="1.2. 使用 sql 片段，第一次听说"></a>1.2. 使用 sql 片段，第一次听说</h5><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/x8b9jd2p/image-20221214163707254.png" alt="image-20221214163707254"></p><h5 id="2-1-使用resultMap映射，column-数据库表中的列名，properties-实体类中的字段名，type-pojo包下对应的实体类，这里是使用了别名"><a href="#2-1-使用resultMap映射，column-数据库表中的列名，properties-实体类中的字段名，type-pojo包下对应的实体类，这里是使用了别名" class="headerlink" title="2.1. 使用resultMap映射，column 数据库表中的列名，properties 实体类中的字段名，type pojo包下对应的实体类，这里是使用了别名"></a>2.1. 使用resultMap映射，column 数据库表中的列名，properties 实体类中的字段名，type pojo包下对应的实体类，这里是使用了别名</h5><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/DzTVLgKg/image-20221214164336357.png" alt="image-20221214164336357"></p><h5 id="2-2-具体使用的步骤"><a href="#2-2-具体使用的步骤" class="headerlink" title="2.2. 具体使用的步骤"></a>2.2. 具体使用的步骤</h5><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/x82Dy3HY/image-20221214164914799.png" alt="image-20221214164914799"></p><h2 id="实现增删改查操作"><a href="#实现增删改查操作" class="headerlink" title="实现增删改查操作"></a><em>实现增删改查操作</em></h2><h4 id="1-resultMap-的小细节"><a href="#1-resultMap-的小细节" class="headerlink" title="1. resultMap 的小细节"></a>1. resultMap 的小细节</h4><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/fRNQ19zk/image-20221214171331331.png" alt="image-20221214171331331"></p><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/T3wFzJ8d/image-20221214171611444.png" alt="image-20221214171611444"></p><h5 id="tips：-转义字符-的快捷生成，大写CD-提示"><a href="#tips：-转义字符-的快捷生成，大写CD-提示" class="headerlink" title="tips： 转义字符   ****的快捷生成，大写CD + 提示"></a>tips： 转义字符   **<!--[CDATA[内容]]-->**的快捷生成，大写CD + 提示</h5><h4 id="2-多条件查询–静态"><a href="#2-多条件查询–静态" class="headerlink" title="2. 多条件查询–静态"></a>2. 多条件查询–静态</h4><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/Jz87WgrN/image-20221214172211981.png" alt="image-20221214172211981"></p><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/BbXxCbLC/image-20221214173644811.png" alt="image-20221214173644811"></p><h4 id="3-多条件查询–动态"><a href="#3-多条件查询–动态" class="headerlink" title="3. 多条件查询–动态"></a>3. 多条件查询–动态</h4><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/gJBSVnkY/image-20221214174012354.png" alt="image-20221214174012354"></p><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/CMQFG11N/image-20221214211816750.png" alt="image-20221214211816750"></p><h2 id="以后有时间再学了，未完待续……"><a href="#以后有时间再学了，未完待续……" class="headerlink" title="以后有时间再学了，未完待续……"></a><em>以后有时间再学了，未完待续……</em></h2>]]></content>
      
      
